title: DDFP 259: Bills EJ Manuel, 'Top 100' reaction
itunes:title: DDFP 259: Bills EJ Manuel, 'Top 100' reaction
description:
Shek and Hank chat with Buffalo Bills quarterback EJ Manuel about new teammate Sammy Watkins, EJ's top three quarterbacks, good body language, Jameis Winston and more. The guys also discuss the latest episode of NFL Network's "The Top 100 Players of 2014", debating Tony Romo's placement and ranking the league's top cornerbacks. Lastly, Shek revisits his 1-on-1 interview with "X-Men: Days of Future Past" star Hugh Jackman aka The Wolverine.
